OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775830266
OL,3,CPawprint of lioness could be used for
OL,4,CNASA's space rover vehicles
OL,6,FThe pawprint of a Longleat Safari Park
OL,7,Flioness could be used to improve the
OL,8,Fgrip of NASA's rover vehicles that
OL,9,Fwork on Mars.
OL,11,FInventor Sunil Dhillon has created
OL,12,Ftyres and treads which replicate the
OL,13,Fpaws of former Queen of the Pride,
OL,14,FMalaika, who died last year just
OL,15,Fbefore her 20th birthday.
OL,17,FIt's hoped they'll improve the grip on
OL,18,Fspace vehicles, but also tractors back
OL,19,Fhere on earth, as farmers tackle
OL,20,Fchanging terrain caused by climate
OL,21,Fchange.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
