OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775830266
OL,3,CPawprint of lioness could be used for
OL,4,CNASA's space rover vehicles
OL,6,FBefore lioness Malaika died, Sunil
OL,7,Falso studied her pack to replicate the
OL,8,Fmovement of their body and limbs to
OL,9,Fimprove the suspension system for a
OL,10,Fvehicle he's creating.
OL,12,FThe Malaika tyre and farming vehicle
OL,13,Fhave been granted a patent, and a
OL,14,Fprototype of the vehicle is due to be
OL,15,Fcreated by July.
OL,17,FSunil said: "The Malaika vehicle opens
OL,18,Fthe doorway to create bio-tractor
OL,19,Fvehicles that will also emulate and
OL,20,Freplicate the biomechanical structure
OL,21,Fand movement from other big cats.
OL,26,@yD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775830266
OL,3,CPawprint of lioness could be used for
OL,4,CNASA's space rover vehicles
OL,6,F"By replicating the movements of
OL,7,FMalaika and other lions, we are
OL,8,Fmaximising tractive force and weight
OL,9,Fdistribution while minimising soil
OL,10,Fcompaction and damage, meaning soil
OL,11,Fecology can be protected.
OL,13,F"We know farmers across Europe face
OL,14,Fextreme changes in their land due to
OL,15,Fclimate change. The tyre features the
OL,16,Ftread pattern and paw shape of the
OL,17,Flion to adapt to different levels of
OL,18,Fsaturation in the land.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775830266
OL,3,CPawprint of lioness could be used for
OL,4,CNASA's space rover vehicles
OL,6,F"The paws of lions are designed to
OL,7,Fsecure traction on multiple surfaces,
OL,8,Fand that is what we have managed to
OL,9,Freplicate which will support all
OL,10,Farable farmers to increase their
OL,11,Fproductivity, preserve soil health and
OL,12,Fproduce higher crop yield without
OL,13,Fexpanding into protected wildlife
OL,14,Fconservation areas."
OL,16,FLongleat says observation data from
OL,17,Fthe Serengeti National Park, showing
OL,18,Fhow African lions can respond to
OL,19,Fnatural environmental fluctuations,
OL,20,Fhas helped with the study.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
