OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775830266
OL,3,CPawprint of lioness could be used for
OL,4,CNASA's space rover vehicles
OL,6,FSunil added: "As Lions are incredibly
OL,7,Fadaptable to fully saturated surfaces,
OL,8,Fdry compacted clay surfaces, and loose
OL,9,Fsandy terrain surfaces, and various
OL,10,Frocky road surfaces, the Malaika
OL,11,Fvehicle shall also be considered as a
OL,12,FMan-driven rover to traverse across
OL,13,Fextra-terrestrial terrain surfaces for
OL,14,FMartian exploration.
OL,16,F"This will allow astronauts to travel
OL,17,Fand adapt to different Martian terrain
OL,18,Fsurfaces with minimum risks of
OL,19,Ftractive and durability deterioration.
OL,26,@nD@NOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775830266
OL,3,CPawprint of lioness could be used for
OL,4,CNASA's space rover vehicles
OL,6,F"It is incredibly exciting and I've
OL,7,Fbeen very privileged to have worked
OL,8,Fwith the keepers at Longleat to study
OL,9,Fthe lions and their movement to be
OL,10,Fable to replicate it in mechanical
OL,11,Fform."
OL,13,FThe prototype tyre also recreates the
OL,14,Fhoneycomb cells created by bees and a
OL,15,Fspider's web to ensure the tyre reacts
OL,16,Fflexibly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
