PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775830266
OL,3,CPawprint of lioness could be used for
OL,4,CNASA's space rover vehicles
OL,6,FDr Tom Lewis, Conservation and
OL,7,FResearch Manager at Longleat, said:
OL,8,F"We've been working with Sunil on his
OL,9,Fnew approach to biomechanics for over
OL,10,Fa year.
OL,12,F"It's fascinating to learn about
OL,13,Fsomething completely outside our usual
OL,14,Fresearch area. Seeing how the project
OL,15,Fhas developed and gone from observing
OL,16,Fthe lions to seeing prototypes is
OL,17,Fincredible.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
